    <h1>Account Deletion — Waterly</h1>
  </header>
  <main>
    <p>
      If you would like to delete your account and all related data from the <strong>Waterly</strong> app,
      please follow the steps below.
    </p>

    <h2>Step 1. Submit a Request</h2>
    <p>
      Send an email to:
      <a href="mailto:gleuvatska.hromada@gmail.com">gleuvatska.hromada@gmail.com</a><br />
      with the subject line: <strong>“Waterly Account Deletion Request”</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>In your email, please include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>the email address linked to your account;</li>
      <li>(optional) your user ID if it is visible in the app.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Step 2. Confirmation</h2>
    <p>
      Once we receive your request, we will verify your information and send a confirmation email.
      After confirmation, your account and associated data will be permanently deleted.
    </p>

    <h2>Data That Will Be Deleted</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>name and email address;</li>
      <li>purchase and usage history of water liters;</li>
      <li>interaction history with vending machines;</li>
      <li>profile information (e.g., photo, preferences, etc.);</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data That May Be Retained</h2>
    <p>
      We may temporarily retain anonymized technical data (such as logs and analytics)
      for up to <strong>30 days</strong> for security and reporting purposes.
    </p>

    <h2>Deletion Timeline</h2>
    <p>
      Complete deletion of your data will be processed within <strong>7 business days</strong>
      after confirmation of your request.
    </p>

    <h2>Developer Information</h2>
